      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "The Servlet API Version to be used is determined by the container. So you need to know which is the traget system. To avoid classpath problems don&#39;t ship the servlet api with our artifact thus mark the depency als &#39;provided&#39; in your pom."
