      "body" : "This answer is almost completely right. The issue: <code>&lt;version&gt;3.1&lt;&#47;version&gt;</code> does not exist: <a href=\"http://mvnrepository.com/artifact/javax.servlet/javax.servlet-api\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">mvnrepository.com/artifact/javax.servlet/javax.servlet-api</a> shows what version <i>do</i> exist. I suggest you edit your answer to <code>3.0.1</code>or <code>3.1.0</code> (I would edit it but edits must be 6+ characters in length)"
