    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Include <code>servlet-api-3.1.jar</code> into your dependencies.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Maven</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code>  &lt;dependency&gt;\n      &lt;groupId&gt;javax.servlet&lt;/groupId&gt;\n      &lt;artifactId&gt;javax.servlet-api&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n      &lt;version&gt;3.1.0&lt;/version&gt;\n      &lt;scope&gt;provided&lt;/scope&gt;\n  &lt;/dependency&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li><p><strong>Gradle</strong></p>\n  <pre class=\"lang-none prettyprint-override\"><code>  configurations {\n      provided\n  }\n  sourceSets {\n      main { compileClasspath += configurations.provided }\n  }\n  dependencies {\n      provided 'javax.servlet:javax.servlet-api:3.1.0'\n  }\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n</ul>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 3324894,
      "reputation" : 207,
      "user_id" : 2795176,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 29,
      "profile_image" : "https://graph.facebook.com/100002409804103/picture?type=large",
      "display_name" : "Anant Pathak",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/2795176/anant-pathak"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 6,
    "last_activity_date" : 1485106027,
    "last_edit_date" : 1485106027,
    "creation_date" : 1402195722,
    "answer_id" : 24102549,
    "question_id" : 22756153,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Select project → <em>Properties</em> → <em>Project Facets</em> → <em>Target Runtimes</em> → <em>VMware Server</em>.</p>\n\n<p>It worked for me.</p>\n"
