    "answer_id" : 28735245,
    "question_id" : 22756153,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Adding the Tomcat server in the server runtime will do the job:</p>\n\n<p>Project properties → <em>Java Build Path</em> → <em>Add Library</em> → <em>Select \"Server Runtime\"</em> from the list → <em>Next</em> → Select \"Apache Tomcat\" → <em>Finish</em>.</p>\n"
