    "question_id" : 22756153,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p><strong>In case of JBoss...</strong> right click on project → <em>Build Java path</em> → add external JAR files.</p>\n\n<p>Then browse to jboss-folder → <em>Common</em> → <em>lib</em> → servlet-api.jar</p>\n\n<p>.\n.\nClick <kbd>OK</kbd>, refresh the project, and run it...</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 4218968,
      "reputation" : 4460,
      "user_id" : 3454208,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 48,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/bRFe3.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "Varun",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/3454208/varun"
